OL,3,CUK-wide strategy needed to tackle
OL,4,Cpensioner poverty, says committee
OL,6,FGiven that the state pension is the
OL,7,Fcore of the Government's offer to
OL,8,Fpensioners, a guiding principle should
OL,9,Fbe that it provides the amount needed
OL,10,Ffor a "minimum, dignified, socially
OL,11,Facceptable standard of living", the
OL,12,Fcommittee said.
OL,14,FIt urged the Government to commit to a
OL,15,FUK-wide, cross-government strategy for
OL,16,Fan ageing society, that it said would
OL,17,Fhelp target support to tackle
OL,18,Fpensioner poverty.
