OL,3,CUK-wide strategy needed to tackle
OL,4,Cpensioner poverty, says committee
OL,6,FIf it does not effectively tackle
OL,7,Fpoverty as one of the causes of ill-
OL,8,Fhealth, "the Government will not be
OL,9,Fable to achieve its goal of building a
OL,10,Fhealth and social care service that is
OL,11,Fsustainable", the Pensioner Poverty
OL,12,Freport warned.
OL,14,FThe report also highlighted longer-
OL,15,Fterm trends that "threaten to
OL,16,Fundermine pension adequacy", such as
OL,17,Fpeople renting into later life.
OL,19,FThe committee also called for a
OL,20,Fpension credit take-up strategy for
OL,21,FEngland by the end of 2025.
