OL,6,FDespite being worth up to #4,000 a
OL,7,Fyear, the take-up of pension credit
OL,8,Fhas hovered between 61% and 66% for a
OL,9,Fdecade, with an estimated 700,000
OL,10,Fhouseholds being eligible but not
OL,11,Fclaiming, the committee said.
OL,13,FA taper to pension credit should also
OL,14,Fbe considered to "mitigate the cliff-
OL,15,Fedge effect" for those who currently
OL,16,Fmiss out, the report said.
OL,18,FUnder current rules, some pensioners
OL,19,Fjust above income thresholds could end
OL,20,Fup worse off than those with slightly
OL,21,Flower incomes, it added.
