OL,6,FPension credit can "passport"
OL,7,Frecipients to other benefits such as
OL,8,Fhousing benefit, council tax support,
OL,9,Fthe warm homes discount, a free TV
OL,10,Flicence, help with dental treatment
OL,11,Fand, in winter 2024/25, the winter
OL,12,Ffuel payment.
