OL,3,CUK-wide strategy needed to tackle
OL,4,Cpensioner poverty, says committee
OL,6,FThe report said: "After a decline in
OL,7,Fpensioner poverty in the 2000s, the
OL,8,Fnumber of pensioners in relative low
OL,9,Fincome started to rise again from
OL,10,F2010. This has been exacerbated by
OL,11,Fincreases in the cost of living since
OL,12,F2021."
OL,14,FIt continued: "The number of people of
OL,15,Fpension age living in relative poverty
OL,16,F(below 60% of median income) is 1.9
OL,17,Fmillion or 16% of pensioners.
