OL,9,Fhouseholds below the Minimum Income
OL,10,FStandard (MIS)`the amount needed for a
OL,11,Fminimum dignified socially acceptable
OL,12,Fstandard of living`rose from 1.5 to
OL,13,F2.8 million.
