OL,6,FCommittee chairwoman Debbie Abrahams
OL,7,Fsaid: "To boost incomes, the
OL,8,FGovernment needs to come up with a
OL,9,Fstrategy to increase pension credit
OL,10,Ftake-up. It's a scandal that so many
OL,11,Fhave missed out for so many years,
OL,12,Foften through an aversion to claiming
OL,13,Fbenefits altogether, or lack of
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,F"The fairness of the pensions credit
OL,17,Feligibility criteria where if you are
OL,18,Fa penny above the threshold, you miss
OL,19,Fout on thousands of pounds, also needs
OL,20,Fto be looked at.
