OL,3,CUK-wide strategy needed to tackle
OL,4,Cpensioner poverty, says committee
OL,6,F"Faced with a combination of high
OL,7,Fenergy costs, ill-health and ever
OL,8,Fhigher rates of pensioners in more
OL,9,Fcostly privately rented accommodation,
OL,10,Ftackling pensioner poverty is not
OL,11,Fsimply a DWP (Department for Work and
OL,12,FPensions) issue. So, we're calling for
OL,13,Fa nationwide, cross-government
OL,14,Fstrategy for an ageing society that
OL,15,Fshould be rooted in equity and
OL,16,Fwellbeing."
